data.description: South Coconut Creek Jewel! This amazing, renovated pool home checks all your boxes for your perfect home.  Home has 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms split floor plan with living room/dining room concept, laminate flooring throughout. The kitchen features stainless steel appliances & granite countertops.  Open your French doors to your pool oasis backyard.  This home features gates on either side of the home to store the RV & boat on the premises. No HOA! Amazing family-friendly neighborhood with sidewalks, a boat ramp, parks with tennis courts, a playground, volleyball, & walking paths.  Large community center with fitness room & basketball courts.  Walking distance to Coconut Creek Elemen, Coconut Creek High School, & Broward College North Campus.
